@context: Rahul Shetty Academy Practice Page
@blueprint: complex_ui_inspector

# 🐾 RAHUL SHETTY HUNT: The Real Inspector Challenge
# Перевірка радіо-кнопок, автозаповнення, таблиць та ховерів.

1. NAVIGATE to https://rahulshettyacademy.com/AutomationPractice/

# ── Radio buttons ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
2. Click the radio button for 'Radio1'
3. VERIFY that 'Radio1' is checked.
4. Click the radio button for 'Radio3'
5. VERIFY that 'Radio3' is checked.

# ── Autocomplete / suggestion field ───────────────────────────────
6. Fill 'Suggession Class' field with 'Ukra'
7. Click 'Ukraine' in the suggestion list
8. VERIFY that 'Ukraine' is present.

# ── Dropdown ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
9. Select 'Option1' from the 'Dropdown' list
10. Select 'Option2' from the 'Dropdown' list
11. Select 'Option3' from the 'Dropdown' list

# ── Checkboxes ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
12. Click the checkbox for 'Option1'
13. VERIFY that 'Option1' is checked.
14. Click the checkbox for 'Option2'
15. VERIFY that 'Option2' is checked.
16. Click the checkbox for 'Option3'
17. VERIFY that 'Option3' is checked.
18. Click the checkbox for 'Option1'
19. VERIFY that 'Option1' is not checked.

# ── Name field + alert confirm ─────────────────────────────────────
20. Fill 'Enter Your Name' field with 'Cyber Manul'
21. VERIFY that 'Cyber Manul' is present.
22. Click the 'Confirm' button
23. VERIFY that 'Cyber Manul' is NOT present.

# ── SCROLL + data extraction from table ───────────────────────────
24. SCROLL DOWN
25. EXTRACT the Price of 'Selenium' into {selenium_price}
26. EXTRACT the Price of 'Appium' into {appium_price}
27. EXTRACT the Price of 'Learn SQL' into {sql_price}
28. VERIFY that '25' is present.

# ── Hide / Show ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
29. Fill 'Hide/Show Example' field with 'Ghost Mode'
30. VERIFY that 'Ghost Mode' is present.
31. Click the 'Hide' button
32. VERIFY that 'Ghost Mode' is NOT present.
33. Click the 'Show' button
34. VERIFY that 'Ghost Mode' is present.

# ── Dynamic table ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
35. SCROLL DOWN
36. EXTRACT the Amount of 'Jack' into {jack_amount}
37. EXTRACT the Amount of 'Joe' into {joe_amount}
38. VERIFY that 'Joe' is present.

# ── Mouse hover ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
39. HOVER over the 'Mouse Hover' button
40. VERIFY that 'Reload' is present.
41. VERIFY that 'Top' is present.

# ── Back to top ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
42. Click the 'Top' link in the menu
43. VERIFY that 'Practice Page' is present.

44. DONE.